$Id: README,v 1.1 2002/10/25 15:49:28 reggers Exp reggers $

This module, Apache::AuthenPOP3, is an Apache/mod_perl authentication handler
to authenticate users using a POP3 mail server. Cf. Apache::AuthenIMAP

To build and install it, please run

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make install

To read more about this module try

    pod2text AuthenPOP3.pm 

